quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  45,23,"Then have you seen him who takes his desire for his god while Allah has left him to stray on (the basis of his) knowledge, and has set a seal on his hearing and his heart and has placed a covering on his sight? So who can guide him after Allah? Will you not then be mindful"
  45,24,"And they say, “There is nothing but our life of this world, we die and we live and nothing destroys us but time,” and they have no knowledge of that, they do nothing but guess"
  45,25,"And when Our clear signs are recited to them, their argument is nothing but that they say, “Bring (back) our fathers, if you are the truthful ones.” are the truthful ones.”"
  45,26,"Say, “Allah gives you life then He causes you to die, then He will gather you towards the day of resurrection, about which there is no doubt, but the majority of human beings does not know.”"
  45,27,"And Allah’s is the kingdom of the skies and the earth. And the day the hour of doom will be established, on that day, those who followed falsehood will be at a loss"
  45,28,"And you will see every community kneeling, every community will be called towards its record, this day you are rewarded for that which you used to do"
  45,29,This is Our record which speaks about you with truth. We certainly got recorded that which you used to do
  45,30,"Then as for those who believed and did righteous works, their Fosterer will make them enter into His mercy, that is a dear achievement"
  45,31,"And as for those who did not believe, (it will be said), “Then were not Our signs recited to you? But you considered yourselves great and you were a criminal people.”"
  45,32,"And when it was said, “The promise of Allah is certainly true and the hour of doom, there is no doubt about it, ”you said, “We do not know what the hour of doom is, we think that it is nothing but a guess and we are not of those who are certain (about it).”"